Step -1 upadte the Apt

       sudo apt-get update

Step -2 PHP installing .deb packages.

       sudo add-apt-repository ppa:ondrej/php

Step -3 set the repository 

       sudo apt-get install php8.0 -y

Step -4 reboot the apache server.

       sudo systemctl restart apache2

step -5  restart automatically when the system reboots.

      sudo systemctl enable apache2

step -6 check version

        php -v

step -9 update php info file

      sudo vi /var/www/info.php

